datasourceConfigModel.description: Select an Analytics Account from the drop-down list.

queries.errorMessage:
Here are two suggestions:

1. Make sure you have access to your company's Google Analytics account.

2. From time to time, your Google token will expire. This token allows you to safely bring your data into Klipfolio. Find out how to re-authorize your OAuth tokens.
